text: On my way to the clan rally to celebrate my highest kill talent, a grand finale to this day before I load up an ammo and go on a killing speech tomorrow. But while driving my Tahoe, my GTS miscalculated directions, created a path through the wrong neighborhood I glanced over and there they stood, a group of emaciated men addicted to wood. That's right, I was staring straight at a pack of fangs. This was sending red flags, somehow I drove into Clear Street, grabbed my walk in the heartbeat, the clan rally had to wait. My priority was to kill this group of eight as bandits who were underway, probably from the HIV infecting their bodies and mind. So I walked behind one of the cockjockies and blew out his brains adrenaline rushing through my veins trampled over the death fangs remains and fired into the backs of the shitstabbers hauling ass from the scene, but their ass was grass if you know what I mean. True blind-stropping like craze, mowing down daisies, my vision was hazy because I was a little bit smoked some good shit beforehand. But I still managed to blow away the gaze, wrapping the trip okay, my lunar abilities on display. Managed to find a rally before it ended, and despite not arriving at the time intended it was splendid, but driving on to Clear Street wasn't so bad executing home OS's wrath. Next time I'll get here a tad bit earlier so I don't miss much of the rally I should travel to South Cali for my summer vacation. I hear it's the game as part of the nation. More Clear Streets for me to wipe out I just hope my GPS knows the route. I can't burn a Vino Will look like child's play after the moon rises.
